name: LoL Game Stats
body:
### What is it?
LoL Game Stats hosts a socket server and can notify clients when game events happen

### Works with
* [Dream Stream](http://suentiem.github.io/Dream-Stream/)

### Installing
* Download main.exe
* Run main.exe

### Supported Events
* Game Load
* Game Start
* Game End
* Team Kill
* Team Death
* Kill
* Death
* Assist
* CS
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
